# FinanceTrackerAPI

A RESTful API built with ASP.NET Core 8 and SQLite for tracking personal finances.

## Features
- Add, edit, delete expenses
- Categorize expenses (Food, Transport, etc.)
- Monthly summary with totals by category
- Persistent storage with SQLite database

## Tech Stack
- C# / ASP.NET Core 8
- Entity Framework Core
- SQLite
- Swagger UI

## Endpoints
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| GET | /api/expenses | Get all expenses |
| POST | /api/expenses | Add new expense |
| PUT | /api/expenses/{id} | Edit expense |
| DELETE | /api/expenses/{id} | Delete expense |
| GET | /api/expenses/summary | Monthly summary by category |

## How to Run
1. Clone the repo
2. Open in Visual Studio 2022
3. Run the project
4. Navigate to https://localhost:{port}/swagger
